{
  "title": "ISic001694. Fragment of a public inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/KAIR5ZLR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/KAIR5ZLR</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 1<br></span>  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"α\">α</span> καὶ <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΙΕΡΑΣ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Τ̣ΟΝ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΩΣ <span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 2<br></span>  <br id=\"al1-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΠΤ̣[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΜΑΙΜ̣[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>τῶν <span data-text=\"δ\">δ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ον\">ον</span> ἀπὸ <span data-text=\"τ\">τ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"ρους\">ρους</span> ΤΙΑ̣[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/KAIR5ZLR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/KAIR5ZLR</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 1<br></span><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"α\">Α</span>ΚΑΙ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΙΕΡΑΣ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>].ΟΝ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΩΣ<span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 2<br></span><br id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Π.[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΜΑΙ.[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΤΩΝ<span data-text=\"δ\">Δ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ον\">ΟΝ</span>ΑΠΟ<span data-text=\"τ\">Τ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"ρους\">ΡΟΥΣ</span>ΤΙ.[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Arena 2020</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Arena 2020 75-81 no. 5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002404\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002404</a></li></ul>  <ul><li>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Arena notes that the quadrangular module of the individual letters is somewhat irregular, with the combined module of omicron-nu (used as a control across multiple similar fragments) being 10mm from centre to centre. Letters with neat terminal serifs, elegantly cut.</p> Line 1-5  8  Interlineation  6  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
